OL,3,C'l'll always try my best': Green MP
OL,4,CHannah Spencer heads to Westminster
OL,6,F"I will always do you proud": MP
OL,7,FHannah Spencer travels to London for
OL,8,Fher first week in Parliament.
OL,10,FThe new Green MP for Gorton and Denton
OL,11,Fhas promised to make her constituents
OL,12,Fproud as she prepares to take her seat
OL,13,Fin Parliament following her historic
OL,14,Fvictory at the polls.
OL,16,FHannah Spencer, who was until recently
OL,17,Fa plumber, travelled to Westminster on
OL,18,FSunday evening after winning the
OL,19,FGreater Manchester seat on Friday, 27
OL,20,FFebruary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
