OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772447794
OL,3,C'l'll always try my best': Green MP
OL,4,CHannah Spencer heads to Westminster
OL,6,FHer victory in the by-election - where
OL,7,Fshe overturned a 13,000-vote Labour
OL,8,Fmajority - has made her the first
OL,9,FGreen MP in the North West and only
OL,10,Fthe seventh in the party's history.
OL,12,FAs she prepared for her journey from
OL,13,FStockport to London, Hannah thanked
OL,14,Fthe constituents who voted for her and
OL,15,Fsaid: "You are the reason why so many
OL,16,Fof us try the very best we can to make
OL,17,Fa better world.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772447794
OL,3,C'l'll always try my best': Green MP
OL,4,CHannah Spencer heads to Westminster
OL,6,F"None of us are perfect but we're
OL,7,Fhuman and we need more humans in
OL,8,Fparliament who care about each other.
OL,9,FI promise to always do my best, and
OL,10,Falways be decent, and I will always do
OL,11,Fyou proud."
OL,13,FSpencer, who was a councillor in
OL,14,FTrafford, had virtually no name
OL,15,Frecognition in Gorton and Denton until
OL,16,Fa month ago when she was announced as
OL,17,Fthe Green Party candidate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
