OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772447794
OL,3,C'l'll always try my best': Green MP
OL,4,CHannah Spencer heads to Westminster
OL,6,FBut she sailed to victory in the by-
OL,7,Felection that was called when the
OL,8,Farea's former MP Andrew Gwynne stood
OL,9,Fdown from the role because of
OL,10,F"significant ill health."
OL,12,FIn her victory speech, the politician
OL,13,Femphasised her working-class roots,
OL,14,Fstating: "Working hard used to get you
OL,15,Fa house, a nice life, holidays. Now,
OL,16,Fit feels like we're just working to
OL,17,Fline the pockets of billionaires."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
