OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772447794
OL,3,C'l'll always try my best': Green MP
OL,4,CHannah Spencer heads to Westminster
OL,6,FShe added: "I'm not here to be a
OL,7,Fcareer politician," she insisted. "I'm
OL,8,Fhere to hold the door open for others
OL,9,Fwho do jobs like mine."
OL,11,FHannah Spencer claimed 4,980 votes and
OL,12,Fa majority of 4,402 votes.
OL,14,FReform UK's candidate Matt Goodwin got
OL,15,F10,578 votes, with Labour's Angeliki
OL,16,FStogia trailing on 9,364, down from
OL,17,F18,555 in the 2024 general election,
OL,18,Fwhen the turnout was similarly high.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
